WEBVTT

00:00:12.438 --> 00:00:14.646
SHEN-LUNG TEMPLE

00:00:14.730 --> 00:00:17.771
SHEN-LUNG WATER

00:00:17.855 --> 00:00:20.063
INFINITE LIFE

00:00:20.146 --> 00:00:22.688
LIFE

00:00:22.771 --> 00:00:25.480
SHEN-LUNG TEMPLE

00:00:27.688 --> 00:00:29.271
-Is that him?
-Yes.

00:00:30.313 --> 00:00:32.896
Stealing my money's one thing,
but fucking my wife?

00:00:33.563 --> 00:00:35.813
You scammer. Let's go!

00:00:49.980 --> 00:00:53.188
Shen-Lung Crown Prince, you're dying.

00:00:53.980 --> 00:00:57.813
I can save you.
But you must pay the price.

00:00:59.396 --> 00:01:00.855
Just take my hand,

00:01:01.855 --> 00:01:04.271
and your fate will be changed.

00:01:28.438 --> 00:01:31.230
AGENT FROM ABOVE

00:01:33.063 --> 00:01:36.563
SOUL HARVEST

00:01:37.063 --> 00:01:39.063
DONGFENG MARKET

00:01:58.771 --> 00:02:01.021
Everyone, time to eat.

00:02:03.688 --> 00:02:05.438
-Thank you.
-Wow, what a feast.

00:02:06.021 --> 00:02:07.521
What a feast.

00:02:07.605 --> 00:02:09.563
Oh my god, that really hits the spot.

00:02:09.646 --> 00:02:11.855
-It's delicious!
-Have as much as you want.

00:02:11.938 --> 00:02:14.688
Welcome, new neighbors.
Anything you'd like, I can cook.

00:02:14.771 --> 00:02:16.188
-You're so nice.
-Get me one.

00:02:16.271 --> 00:02:19.938
-There's plenty. Help yourselves.
-You're too kind.

00:02:20.021 --> 00:02:22.105
We've got desserts and snacks here.

00:02:22.188 --> 00:02:23.146
C cup?

00:02:26.521 --> 00:02:28.980
Hi, I'm Mei-na. Welcome to the community.

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:30.813
Hi, I'm Wang Hsiao-ming.

00:02:31.521 --> 00:02:33.188
Interested in a ghost marriage?

00:02:45.896 --> 00:02:46.855
Wang Hsiao-ming.

00:02:50.813 --> 00:02:51.896
What's up?

00:02:52.396 --> 00:02:53.396
Take your pick.

00:02:56.396 --> 00:02:58.396
I can't believe it!

00:03:00.271 --> 00:03:01.480
You shouldn't have.

00:03:01.563 --> 00:03:04.938
That one's no good.
But the suit has style.

00:03:05.021 --> 00:03:08.271
Nah, makes no difference.
He looks tacky in anything.

00:03:08.355 --> 00:03:09.438
Madam.

00:03:09.521 --> 00:03:13.188
You shouldn't give him such a hard time.
Let's go try on the clothes.

00:03:13.771 --> 00:03:14.896
Get changed together?

00:03:14.980 --> 00:03:18.105
-Together?
-You two together? Don't you dare.

00:03:18.188 --> 00:03:19.980
-Why don't you join us?
-Hurry up.

00:03:21.146 --> 00:03:24.896
Han Chieh, have you seen Ms. Chiang?
She moved in next to you last week.

00:03:26.896 --> 00:03:30.146
No, but I've seen her daughter.
I think she might be deaf.

00:03:31.396 --> 00:03:34.355
Seems Ms. Chiang has had a hard life.

00:03:34.938 --> 00:03:38.188
Oh well. I'll invite her
to dinner at my restaurant.

00:03:38.813 --> 00:03:42.063
And you should check in on her
when you have time.

00:03:48.313 --> 00:03:49.146
Everyone.

00:03:52.646 --> 00:03:54.896
Oh my, Wang Hsiao-ming.

00:03:54.980 --> 00:03:56.646
Is that you, Wang Hsiao-ming?

00:03:56.730 --> 00:03:59.063
-He looks so old.
-Like a sleazy old man.

00:03:59.146 --> 00:04:00.896
-No, he doesn't.
-Grandpa Wang.

00:04:01.730 --> 00:04:04.021
-Grandpa Wang.
-Hsiao-ming, you look sublime,

00:04:04.105 --> 00:04:05.855
but aren't worth a dime.

00:04:07.230 --> 00:04:08.896
Everyone's getting along so well.

00:04:13.980 --> 00:04:15.855
Thanks to the old guard and Sister Lo.

00:04:18.521 --> 00:04:21.313
Did their families die in that fire too?

00:04:21.396 --> 00:04:22.480
Yeah.

00:04:23.646 --> 00:04:26.605
Sis Lo's younger brother
and the old guard's son and grandson.

00:04:28.188 --> 00:04:30.063
They all wanted to stay together,

00:04:30.855 --> 00:04:32.271
so I opened their third eyes.

00:04:34.938 --> 00:04:37.896
But Sis Lo's younger brother
never showed up.

00:04:40.313 --> 00:04:42.146
I hope she can move on soon.

00:04:45.896 --> 00:04:46.730
Han Chieh.

00:04:46.813 --> 00:04:50.271
You might seem cold on the outside,
but you're a good guy really.

00:04:55.105 --> 00:04:58.730
You spend all your time here.
Still taking your medication?

00:04:59.605 --> 00:05:00.605
Of course.

00:05:03.521 --> 00:05:04.896
Han Chieh, smile.

00:05:08.188 --> 00:05:09.230
What are you doing?

00:05:22.188 --> 00:05:25.313
A gang called the Heilung Clan
was wiped out last night.

00:05:25.396 --> 00:05:28.730
They died insane deaths.
I'll drop by tomorrow. Help me out.

00:05:30.855 --> 00:05:33.980
BLESS THIS HOUSEHOLD

00:05:40.355 --> 00:05:42.896
Seems Ms. Chiang has had a hard life.

00:05:42.980 --> 00:05:45.146
Check in on her when you have time.

00:05:49.188 --> 00:05:52.105
I'm Han Chieh. I live next door.

00:05:53.771 --> 00:05:56.771
Sister Lo mentioned you.
You're the agent from above, right?

00:06:01.271 --> 00:06:05.146
Everyone's having dinner on the rooftop.
Sister Lo was asking about you.

00:06:05.230 --> 00:06:07.688
-Why don't you take your daughter?
-I couldn't.

00:06:07.771 --> 00:06:10.646
Yuan-yuan is deaf and can't speak.
I don't want to impose.

00:06:12.230 --> 00:06:13.563
I saw her a few days ago.

00:06:14.480 --> 00:06:17.105
She loves to draw and is such a cute kid.

00:06:41.355 --> 00:06:42.355
I'll leave you to it.

00:06:42.938 --> 00:06:44.396
Master Han.

00:06:44.480 --> 00:06:47.563
I've been ill for years
and my daughter is deaf.

00:06:47.646 --> 00:06:50.063
-Do you know of any…
-I'm not some master.

00:06:51.855 --> 00:06:53.230
I'm just an ordinary guy.

00:06:55.146 --> 00:06:55.980
I'm sorry.

00:07:10.105 --> 00:07:10.938
LINGERING SPIRIT

00:07:14.730 --> 00:07:17.730
SHEN-LUNG CROWN PRINCE
FORCED BY OCCULTIST TO COMMIT CRIMES

00:07:52.188 --> 00:07:54.813
TEMPLE FIRE CLAIMS TWO LIVES

00:07:54.896 --> 00:07:56.230
FENGYUAN TEMPLE

00:08:00.646 --> 00:08:02.438
TEMPLE EVICTION DISPUTE TURNS FATAL

00:08:02.521 --> 00:08:05.938
LIU KUAN-FU DENIES INVOLVEMENT

00:08:06.521 --> 00:08:08.771
TEMPLE ARSON LINKED TO LAND DISPUTE?

00:08:08.855 --> 00:08:10.896
LIU KUAN-FU: "WHERE'S THE PROOF?"

00:08:14.313 --> 00:08:18.271
"WHERE'S THE PROOF?"

00:08:26.146 --> 00:08:27.896
CHANG MIN

00:08:37.438 --> 00:08:38.980
Why didn't you take my call?

00:08:40.355 --> 00:08:42.105
You never have good news.

00:08:42.688 --> 00:08:43.521
Hey.

00:08:44.605 --> 00:08:45.480
Look.

00:08:49.271 --> 00:08:50.396
The Demon King?

00:08:51.730 --> 00:08:54.646
Eleven members
of the Heilung Clan taken out like this.

00:08:59.188 --> 00:09:00.563
Chen Chi-sha?

00:09:01.063 --> 00:09:04.396
They had lots of enemies.
Anyone could have hired a hitman.

00:09:05.188 --> 00:09:09.271
Chen Chi-sha wouldn't kill for money.
And why's the Demon King's symbol there?

00:09:10.855 --> 00:09:12.813
No way this was just triads feuding.

00:09:19.563 --> 00:09:22.730
Don't say I didn't warn you
when the shit hits the fan.

00:09:26.230 --> 00:09:28.313
I know a guy
who used to run with the triads.

00:09:28.396 --> 00:09:31.021
I'll go sound him out.
Maybe he knows something.

00:09:32.980 --> 00:09:33.813
This way.

00:09:33.896 --> 00:09:34.938
-Fu.
-Have a seat.

00:09:35.021 --> 00:09:37.855
You've done well for yourself?
The temple's huge now.

00:09:38.355 --> 00:09:40.105
Not back in that business, are you?

00:09:40.771 --> 00:09:43.646
Of course not.
Han Chieh, you've got it all wrong.

00:09:43.730 --> 00:09:46.563
Hey, I don't give out false tips

00:09:46.646 --> 00:09:48.855
or run scams on people anymore.

00:09:48.938 --> 00:09:51.521
All the money
comes from donations to the temple.

00:09:51.605 --> 00:09:54.521
I take a cut for expenses,
then donate the rest to charity.

00:09:55.855 --> 00:09:58.813
I even help clean the beach
and feed the homeless.

00:10:01.605 --> 00:10:03.563
-I'll get the account books.
-No need.

00:10:04.438 --> 00:10:05.980
This isn't about you.

00:10:09.605 --> 00:10:11.480
That thing I asked you to look into?

00:10:18.271 --> 00:10:22.105
So, a friend at another temple told me

00:10:22.605 --> 00:10:26.605
that the Heilung Clan won a 100 million
government construction project.

00:10:26.688 --> 00:10:29.730
Liu Kuan-fu and the Heilung Clan
had a deal.

00:10:29.813 --> 00:10:34.313
The Heilung Clan would subcontract
the work to Liu Kuan-fu's supplier.

00:10:34.396 --> 00:10:36.938
Maybe they fell out
over the split or whatever,

00:10:37.021 --> 00:10:39.230
but the Heilung Clan took the lot.

00:10:44.438 --> 00:10:49.438
Everyone knew they hated each other.
It was bound to happen sooner or later.

00:10:49.521 --> 00:10:53.605
It's just… I never thought Liu Kuan-fu
would be quite so ruthless.

00:10:53.688 --> 00:10:54.896
Ruthless?

00:10:56.021 --> 00:10:57.355
Of course he's ruthless.

00:10:58.438 --> 00:11:01.355
He took the deeds
to our little temple and set it on fire.

00:11:01.980 --> 00:11:05.855
He got me addicted to drugs
so he could take my family's land.

00:11:06.896 --> 00:11:08.521
He made sure I owed him big.

00:11:09.521 --> 00:11:10.896
FENGYUAN TEMPLE

00:11:11.855 --> 00:11:15.230
Then he tricked me into handing over
the deeds as collateral.

00:11:26.855 --> 00:11:30.438
LAND OWNERSHIP CERTIFICATE

00:11:32.396 --> 00:11:33.605
Kneel!

00:11:33.688 --> 00:11:36.021
Tell the Third Crown Prince
what you've done.

00:11:36.105 --> 00:11:39.271
The construction company
says our land is theirs now!

00:11:39.355 --> 00:11:41.521
-You'll be the death of me!
-That's enough.

00:11:41.605 --> 00:11:43.730
I wish you'd never been born!

00:11:43.813 --> 00:11:44.855
Stop it!

00:11:51.771 --> 00:11:53.188
My dad wouldn't cooperate,

00:11:53.688 --> 00:11:56.230
so Liu Kuan-fu burned the place down.

00:11:57.063 --> 00:11:59.271
-How could this happen?
-Our stuff is inside.

00:11:59.355 --> 00:12:03.021
Did anyone get out?
The fire suddenly broke out.

00:12:03.105 --> 00:12:04.813
Heavens, what should we do?

00:12:06.605 --> 00:12:08.980
-Hey!
-Calm down!

00:12:27.688 --> 00:12:29.188
FENGYUAN TEMPLE

00:12:29.271 --> 00:12:30.396
In the end,

00:12:30.896 --> 00:12:35.813
both my mom and dad perished in that fire.

00:12:46.105 --> 00:12:49.188
They've been in hell ever since
suffering because of me.

00:12:53.646 --> 00:12:55.605
My boss wants me to kill evil ghosts.

00:12:56.730 --> 00:12:58.855
But if someone is even worse than a ghost,

00:12:59.355 --> 00:13:01.855
how could killing them violate my orders?

00:13:07.980 --> 00:13:09.855
I know it sucks.

00:13:10.605 --> 00:13:12.730
But he gave you a chance
to redeem yourself

00:13:12.813 --> 00:13:14.855
because he knows what you've been through.

00:13:14.938 --> 00:13:16.313
It's a big responsibility.

00:13:17.896 --> 00:13:18.896
As if.

00:13:20.230 --> 00:13:21.813
Don't be like that. Hey.

00:13:22.605 --> 00:13:24.146
Have you seen the Marvel movies?

00:13:24.230 --> 00:13:27.813
Ever see Iron Man
kill without good reason?

00:13:27.896 --> 00:13:30.980
Iron Man only became a hero
after he redeemed himself.

00:13:31.063 --> 00:13:33.730
You're actually a superhero.

00:13:33.813 --> 00:13:36.521
With great power
comes great responsibility.

00:13:36.605 --> 00:13:39.563
If you abuse your power,
you're no better than Liu Kuan-fu.

00:13:42.188 --> 00:13:43.813
If I'm a superhero, what are you?

00:13:45.730 --> 00:13:46.730
Me?

00:13:49.480 --> 00:13:50.396
I'm this guy.

00:13:56.230 --> 00:13:57.230
A truck driver?

00:13:59.188 --> 00:14:01.688
Come on. I'm Doctor Strange.

00:14:01.771 --> 00:14:04.438
Don't you see it? I'm Doctor Strange.

00:14:04.938 --> 00:14:05.771
Hey.

00:14:06.271 --> 00:14:07.105
Hey.

00:14:07.605 --> 00:14:10.896
It does look like I'm driving.
Hey, wait for me.

00:14:18.771 --> 00:14:19.605
Boss.

00:14:25.521 --> 00:14:29.646
Boss, why'd Chen Chi-sha want to meet
out here in the middle of nowhere?

00:14:29.730 --> 00:14:31.146
What's his game?

00:14:31.813 --> 00:14:32.938
Mr. Liu.

00:14:39.813 --> 00:14:42.146
Hey… the money's all here.

00:14:42.230 --> 00:14:44.063
I didn't do it for the money.

00:14:44.980 --> 00:14:49.730
Those Heilung punks were perfect
for testing my hellspawn on.

00:14:53.480 --> 00:14:54.771
Nasty way to go, right?

00:14:57.105 --> 00:14:58.438
The money's here.

00:14:58.521 --> 00:15:01.021
I don't want anything
to do with you from now on.

00:15:01.730 --> 00:15:04.230
Think you can ditch me so easily?

00:15:05.521 --> 00:15:07.813
When you first came to me,

00:15:07.896 --> 00:15:09.938
you seemed to appreciate my skills.

00:15:14.521 --> 00:15:16.313
Stay away from us from now on!

00:15:16.396 --> 00:15:17.730
-Hand it over…
-Boss.

00:15:17.813 --> 00:15:19.230
-Give him the money.
-Here.

00:16:12.480 --> 00:16:15.980
You came,
so you must have taken care of things?

00:16:16.480 --> 00:16:18.730
I'm old, getting rusty.

00:16:22.896 --> 00:16:24.355
You're too modest.

00:16:27.438 --> 00:16:31.438
Anyone chosen by the Demon King
is someone to be reckoned with.

00:16:35.438 --> 00:16:40.063
The way your hellspawn took out
those Heilung punks was terrifying.

00:16:48.605 --> 00:16:52.230
I only worked for the Demon King
to get revenge.

00:16:53.146 --> 00:16:54.730
Triads killed my family.

00:16:55.313 --> 00:16:57.146
They don't deserve to live.

00:16:57.730 --> 00:16:59.146
But this is different.

00:16:59.771 --> 00:17:03.855
You two are working together
to control me and forcing me to kill.

00:17:04.855 --> 00:17:09.563
I know I'm beyond pardon,
but I never killed innocent people before.

00:17:10.855 --> 00:17:12.480
As an evil person,

00:17:12.980 --> 00:17:16.271
I know that evil has many faces.

00:17:18.021 --> 00:17:20.855
But you and I are different.

00:17:29.146 --> 00:17:32.105
What do you want from me next?

00:17:44.438 --> 00:17:45.521
CHIANG HUA-CHIH

00:17:46.230 --> 00:17:50.313
Based on the birth chart,
your illness and your daughter's condition

00:17:50.396 --> 00:17:51.771
are predestined.

00:17:53.605 --> 00:17:57.021
Master, can't I change my destiny?

00:17:57.105 --> 00:17:59.688
A person's destiny
is determined by their birth.

00:18:00.188 --> 00:18:01.188
It can't be changed.

00:18:11.438 --> 00:18:12.938
However…

00:18:13.521 --> 00:18:16.105
there is a way to eliminate bad karma.

00:18:16.188 --> 00:18:17.105
Really?

00:18:18.105 --> 00:18:19.521
How?

00:18:21.480 --> 00:18:22.480
Shen-Lung Crown Prince.

00:18:27.980 --> 00:18:31.980
What do you get as a petty fraudster,
sex and money?

00:18:33.105 --> 00:18:34.938
If you work for me,

00:18:35.730 --> 00:18:37.855
I'll give you everything you want.

00:18:39.521 --> 00:18:40.646
What do I need to do?

00:18:57.105 --> 00:18:58.896
Have you brought your daughter?

00:19:01.021 --> 00:19:03.063
Master.

00:19:03.563 --> 00:19:04.771
I have.

00:19:05.355 --> 00:19:08.063
I didn't tell you this last time,

00:19:08.771 --> 00:19:12.438
but there is a strong
negative energy in your home.

00:19:13.855 --> 00:19:17.563
Someone close to you
is most likely causing you harm.

00:19:19.938 --> 00:19:21.480
When was your daughter born?

00:19:23.105 --> 00:19:25.730
She was born on February 21st, 2009.

00:19:27.188 --> 00:19:28.355
FEBRUARY 21ST, 2009, OX

00:19:28.438 --> 00:19:32.313
February 21st, 2009. Year of the Ox?

00:19:33.438 --> 00:19:37.271
I need some hellspawn
refined from people's primal souls.

00:19:37.855 --> 00:19:40.063
Find me people born on this day…

00:19:40.146 --> 00:19:41.605
FEBRUARY 21ST, 2009, OX

00:19:41.688 --> 00:19:43.063
…and kill them.

00:19:45.063 --> 00:19:46.230
Listen.

00:19:46.313 --> 00:19:48.438
Your daughter is the one

00:19:48.521 --> 00:19:50.563
hindering your recovery.

00:19:51.230 --> 00:19:53.896
Your birth charts are incompatible.

00:19:53.980 --> 00:19:56.105
She makes you ill and you make her mute.

00:19:56.188 --> 00:19:59.688
That's why she'll never speak
and you'll never recover.

00:20:00.605 --> 00:20:02.313
It can't be my daughter, Master.

00:20:02.396 --> 00:20:03.896
Are… are you sure?

00:20:03.980 --> 00:20:05.938
I'm absolutely certain.

00:20:06.521 --> 00:20:07.730
Then what should I do?

00:20:08.313 --> 00:20:10.146
Step outside. Leave her with me.

00:20:14.146 --> 00:20:15.855
-Just step outside. Get out.
-Wait.

00:20:15.938 --> 00:20:18.188
-What are you going to do to her?
-Get out!

00:20:18.271 --> 00:20:19.771
-Yuan-yuan, come here.
-Get out.

00:20:19.855 --> 00:20:21.271
-Out!
-Yuan-yuan, come here.

00:20:21.355 --> 00:20:22.396
-Get out!
-Yuan-yuan!

00:20:24.230 --> 00:20:27.063
Han Chieh, here's the lighter you wanted.

00:20:57.521 --> 00:20:59.980
SHEN-LUNG CROWN PRINCE HARMS PEOPLE

00:21:01.188 --> 00:21:02.438
Another one.

00:21:03.063 --> 00:21:03.896
What?

00:21:11.230 --> 00:21:13.730
That's the third one
with his name on this month.

00:21:13.813 --> 00:21:15.188
First is for fraud.

00:21:15.271 --> 00:21:17.271
Then for working with an occultist.

00:21:18.271 --> 00:21:22.480
You've been ignoring this for a while now
and it just keeps getting worse.

00:21:24.230 --> 00:21:25.063
So it's my fault?

00:21:25.813 --> 00:21:29.146
I've still got tons of tasks to do.
I can't be in two places at once.

00:21:32.855 --> 00:21:35.105
I can't catch all the scammers out there.

00:21:35.188 --> 00:21:38.188
Now you want me to stop the Demon King.
I'm human, not a god.

00:21:38.271 --> 00:21:40.938
I can barely take care of myself.
Fuck all this shit.

00:21:41.021 --> 00:21:42.063
Fuck it.

00:21:43.646 --> 00:21:45.396
Han Chieh, where are you going?

00:21:58.146 --> 00:21:59.146
Yuan-yuan?

00:21:59.855 --> 00:22:00.896
Han Chieh.

00:22:01.688 --> 00:22:02.563
Why is she…

00:22:27.355 --> 00:22:28.313
Who did this?

00:22:29.980 --> 00:22:30.938
Where's your mom?

00:22:39.980 --> 00:22:42.063
I'm going down to hell. Give me a hand.

00:22:42.146 --> 00:22:42.980
Me?

00:22:47.896 --> 00:22:49.271
I've been there many times.

00:22:49.938 --> 00:22:52.355
I use the milk caps' side effects
to knock myself out.

00:22:56.688 --> 00:22:59.771
Play this music
after I've been under for three minutes.

00:23:01.855 --> 00:23:02.771
Shock me with this.

00:23:12.146 --> 00:23:13.188
I'm counting on you.

00:24:25.438 --> 00:24:26.563
Ms. Chiang.

00:24:31.230 --> 00:24:32.271
What happened?

00:24:32.980 --> 00:24:34.355
I can't find Yuan-yuan.

00:24:34.438 --> 00:24:38.188
I can't find Yuan-yuan anywhere.
She died before I did.

00:24:39.188 --> 00:24:40.480
I can't find her.

00:24:40.563 --> 00:24:41.771
Where's her primal soul?

00:24:43.980 --> 00:24:45.563
I don't know.

00:24:45.646 --> 00:24:48.480
She can't come down here
or be reborn without it.

00:24:49.355 --> 00:24:50.188
Who did this?

00:24:53.521 --> 00:24:54.938
The Shen-Lung Crown Prince.

00:24:55.021 --> 00:24:56.063
Open the door!

00:24:56.146 --> 00:24:57.855
Yuan-yuan!

00:24:58.896 --> 00:25:00.688
Yuan-yuan!

00:25:01.355 --> 00:25:02.480
Yuan-yuan!

00:25:52.230 --> 00:25:54.146
I got my daughter killed.

00:25:55.605 --> 00:25:57.521
And I got myself killed.

00:25:59.813 --> 00:26:02.105
-Where is he?
-In his temple.

00:26:23.355 --> 00:26:24.730
My time's up.

00:26:26.021 --> 00:26:28.688
-Where are you going?
-To throw out the trash.

00:26:35.938 --> 00:26:38.188
How… how will you get there?

00:26:39.605 --> 00:26:42.646
-Are you still alive?
-Strictly speaking, I'm dead right now.

00:26:50.771 --> 00:26:52.188
Who exactly are you?

00:26:54.271 --> 00:26:55.355
I work for him.

00:27:03.105 --> 00:27:04.480
You set it too high.

00:27:05.688 --> 00:27:08.188
You never told me how high to set it.

00:27:09.855 --> 00:27:10.688
Grab me a shirt.

00:27:15.271 --> 00:27:17.396
And the lotus seeds from the fridge.

00:27:33.105 --> 00:27:35.646
Tell Chang Min
there's been a murder at Shen-Lung Temple.

00:27:35.730 --> 00:27:36.688
What about you?

00:27:37.980 --> 00:27:39.521
I'm going to settle a score.

00:27:43.605 --> 00:27:45.855
QIANKUN HOOP

00:27:59.230 --> 00:28:01.313
SHEN-LUNG TEMPLE

00:28:18.605 --> 00:28:20.021
Out!

00:28:22.563 --> 00:28:25.396
Look who it is,
the Third Crown Prince's agent from above.

00:28:25.480 --> 00:28:26.563
I'm honored.

00:28:26.646 --> 00:28:28.355
I'll give you one chance.

00:28:28.438 --> 00:28:30.771
Hand over her primal soul,
and I'll spare you.

00:28:31.480 --> 00:28:33.605
He really is such a spoiled brat.

00:28:33.688 --> 00:28:36.563
Even his agent from above
is just a loudmouthed punk.

00:28:36.646 --> 00:28:37.938
Fine.

00:28:38.021 --> 00:28:39.646
I'll beat you senseless first,

00:28:39.730 --> 00:28:41.646
then make you wish you'd never been born.

00:29:28.771 --> 00:29:29.980
Third Crown Prince!

00:29:30.063 --> 00:29:31.896
Third Crown Prince!

00:29:48.688 --> 00:29:51.396
Tell the big man
to come and collect your corpse.

00:30:18.396 --> 00:30:21.688
Thought you were a badass, huh?
Serves you right for mouthing off.

00:30:22.480 --> 00:30:25.521
You can't even beat a fraudster.
Is that all you've got?

00:30:25.605 --> 00:30:26.813
You think I want this?

00:30:28.438 --> 00:30:31.271
-Where are the milk caps I gave you?
-I used them.

00:30:32.355 --> 00:30:33.480
Didn't you see?

00:30:39.105 --> 00:30:41.855
Those milk caps you gave me
are like playthings to them.

00:30:42.396 --> 00:30:43.688
So you're here to bitch?

00:30:44.271 --> 00:30:48.146
You won't let me smoke or drink.
Just give me something I can work with.

00:30:52.855 --> 00:30:54.938
I don't let you smoke or drink.

00:30:55.438 --> 00:30:57.813
Yet you used the Qiankun Hoop to light up.

00:30:58.313 --> 00:30:59.605
Don't forget,

00:31:00.105 --> 00:31:04.688
the more power I give you,
the more it'll hurt after.

00:31:05.730 --> 00:31:06.980
Never stopped me before.

00:31:13.855 --> 00:31:15.313
I'll give you one more.

00:31:23.896 --> 00:31:26.396
Great. I told you, they don't work on him.

00:31:26.896 --> 00:31:28.313
I blessed this one.

00:31:30.771 --> 00:31:32.271
Are you done yet?

00:31:34.146 --> 00:31:35.438
It's my turn now.

00:33:20.021 --> 00:33:24.021
We've been onto this fraudster for a while
now, but never had any evidence.

00:33:24.105 --> 00:33:26.521
Good thing
the Third Crown Prince tipped you off.

00:33:26.605 --> 00:33:28.521
He won't get away this time.

00:33:30.771 --> 00:33:32.230
I should've seen it sooner.

00:33:37.396 --> 00:33:39.771
SHEN-LUNG TEMPLE

00:33:56.271 --> 00:33:58.105
DONGFENG MARKET

00:34:45.355 --> 00:34:48.730
Yuan-yuan, you can be with your mom now.

00:35:18.521 --> 00:35:21.730
HEAVEN, WIND, WATER

00:35:36.521 --> 00:35:38.563
DAD: EXAM OVER YET?
ARE YOU COMING HOME?

00:35:38.646 --> 00:35:41.271
I'M ALMOST THERE